 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Egemen — Turkish SLM, From Scratch\n",
    "\n",
    "Builds and pre-trains a decoder-only transformer **entirely from scratch** in PyTorch on the Turkish corpus.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Architecture** (LLaMA-style, modern):\n",
    "- RMSNorm (pre-norm)\n",
    "- Rotary Position Embeddings (RoPE)\n",
    "- SwiGLU feed-forward\n",
    "- Causal self-attention\n",
    "\n",
    "**Default size — Egemen-Small (~117M params):**\n",
    "| Param | Value |\n",
    "|-------|-------|\n",
    "| Layers | 12 |\n",
    "| Hidden dim | 768 |\n",
    "| Attention heads | 12 |\n",
    "| Context length | 1024 |\n",
    "| Vocab size | 32 000 (Turkish BPE) |\n",
    "\n",
    "**Target platform:** Kaggle free T4 (16 GB VRAM) — ~2 hrs/epoch, fits 3 epochs in one session."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
